Packaging of Ray for ArchLinux
Copyright(R) 2012 Sébastien Boisvert
Copyright(R) 2012 Maxime Déraspe

Guidelines: https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Creating_Packages

Submission: https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/AUR_User_Guidelines#Submitting_packages

To make the package:

    makepkg -f PKGBUILD

To install them:

    pacman -U *.xz

To test the PKGBUILD:

    namcap PKGBUILD

To test packages:

    namcap *.xz

split packages

	https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/sp/splittest/PKGBUILD
